profile:
Our concrete experience of over 30 years has given B-Ray Construction the know-how  to offer a total site package bid along with our excavation, demolition, and sewer and water main divisions.

Over the years our concrete crews have completed various projects.  They include building foundations, walls, suspended  slabs, water treatment plants, factories, parking garages, strip malls, storm structures such as inlets, box culverts, headwalls, street sidewalks, pavement, curbs, bridge piers, .

B-Ray Construction has also completed many decorative concrete, exposed aggregate, bush hammer and stamped walls, and color concrete pads and walks.
